data.description: Welcome to this spacious well cared for 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch style home in the charming town of Pendergrass. This gorgeous property offers a range of features that are sure to impress. The heart of this home is the beautiful kitchen, which boasts modern appliances, ample pantry space, and gorgeous granite countertops that are both stylish and functional. Stained cabinet and hardwoods throughout.  The open floor plan flows seamlessly into the living room, which provides the space for relaxing or entertaining guests. The bedrooms are spacious and offer plenty of natural light and closet space. One of the standout features of this property is the private fenced backyard on a corner lot, providing extra lot space. The yard has been beautifully maintained and is perfect for entertaining cookouts on the extend patio. Don't miss your chance to own this beautiful ranch style home - schedule a viewing today!
